{"tid":2401714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黃店」BJY關店後發現誠品職員拿走寫上「淋病月娥仆街死及印有警察開槍圖案的甜批 其後放回原位 指會付錢了事","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T09:18:10.000Z","uid":22556,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"5872b831415acf97e414dec815a1e2b8538ddb5e","tid":2401714,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"監守自盜抑或政治審查？在太古誠品生活開業的「黃店」BJY藝術烘焙師，日前關店後，3件分別寫上「淋病月娥」、「仆街死」及印有警察開槍圖案的甜批，被誠品職員擅自取走半個鐘，再放回原位。誠品向店主承認事件，但沒交代取走目的，僅稱會向相關職員作懲處。<br />\n<br />\nJay隨即趕返店舖了解事件，有誠品職員承認曾取走涉事3件甜批，但沒有解釋擅取原因，僅付費了事。其後Jay再向誠品跟進事件，對方亦沒有正面回應，只表示已懲處相關職員，不會有下次。<br />\nJay指，雪櫃除存放涉事三件甜批外，亦有其餘糕點，但沒被取走。她批評事件荒謬，質疑當中是否涉及政治原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/6TX6HS7UEFDUBENWVSDYJ6TOC4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2ziyNwo8Nzv1Zqh-2X-8srjtbDA8TbsOf1Q5Fr8yl9PesRE75wzrH2HM0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2F6TX6HS7UEFDUBENWVSDYJ6TOC4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2ziyNwo8Nzv1Zqh-2X-8srjtbDA8TbsOf1Q5Fr8yl9PesRE75wzrH2HM0&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=37b5d95e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2F6TX6HS7UEFDUBENWVSDYJ6TOC4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2ziyNwo8Nzv1Zqh-2X-8srjtbDA8TbsOf1Q5Fr8yl9PesRE75wzrH2HM0&h=2aea1117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/6TX6HS7UEFDUBENWVSDYJ6TOC4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2ziyNwo8Nzv1Zqh-2X-8srjtbDA8TbsOf1Q5Fr8yl9PesRE75wzrH2HM0</a>"},{"pid":"b9bdd839fa1a0eaa14